## Fintech QA Automation Lab (Payments)
Containerized merchant payment service + Playwright API tests.

### What’s covered
- Health check
- Idempotency (same key returns same payment id)
- Confirm payment creates ledger entry
- Webhook replay protection (no double credit)

### Run locally
```bash
docker compose up --build --exit-code-from tests


